ZH: 这家公司的股票价格一直在上涨。
EN: The stock price of this company has been continuously rising.

ZH: 我买入了这家公司的股份。
EN: I bought shares of this company.

ZH: 他卖出了他所有的股份。
EN: He sold all his stocks.

ZH: 这家企业的股份可以在证券交易所上市。
EN: The shares of this company can be listed on the stock exchange.

ZH: 这只股票的股份非常有价值。
EN: The shares of this stock are very valuable.

ZH: 这家投资公司管理着数百家企业的股份。
EN: This investment firm manages shares of hundreds of companies.

ZH: 她通过购买股份来增加她的财富。
EN: She increases her wealth by purchasing shares.

ZH: 我们应该定期监控我们的股份。
EN: We should monitor our shares regularly.

ZH: 这家公司的股份已经上市交易了十年。
EN: The shares of this company have been publicly traded for ten years.

ZH: 这些股份是从市场上购买的。
EN: These shares were bought from the market.

ZH: 他的股份在这次股市崩盘中贬值了。
EN: His stocks depreciated during this stock market crash.

ZH: 这家公司的股价跌破了每股2美元。
EN: The stock price of this company fell below $2 per share.

ZH: 这笔交易涉及数千份股份。
EN: This transaction involves thousands of shares.

ZH: 这家公司计划发行新的股份。
EN: This company plans to issue new shares.

ZH: 我不再持有这家公司的股份。
EN: I no longer hold any shares of this company.

ZH: 这笔交易使他成为了该公司的股东之一。
EN: This transaction made him one of the shareholders of the company.

ZH: 她在市场上购买了一些股份。
EN: She bought some shares in the market.

ZH: 这次合并将使两家公司的股份合并为一家公司的股份。
EN: This merger will combine the shares of two companies into one.

ZH: 这些股份将分配给公司的员工。
EN: These shares will be distributed to the employees of the company.

ZH: 我们需要投资更多的资金购买股份。
EN: We need to invest more funds to purchase shares.
